# REFACTORING

    * CTK::Arc: fextract, fcompress - It is necessary to use FILEGLOB (#367). See fjoin for example

    * CTK::Crypt: gpg_decript - It is necessary to use FILEGLOB (#367). See fjoin for example

    * CTK::File: fsplit, fcopy, fmove, fdelete - It is necessary to use FILEGLOB (#367). See fjoin for example

    * CTK::Net: fetch, store - It is necessary to use FILEGLOB (#367). See fjoin for example

